{"id": 2567, "genre": 1001, "title": "什么情况下你不愿意把你住的地方称为「家」？", "description": "说不清什么样的地方才能叫「家」，但是现在住的地方总不愿意把它称为家。", "record_count": 2560, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181015172649kC3nMVOYL9TQ5Axf.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-10-17T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 304896, "content": "那里就我自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1429465}, {"id": 304897, "content": "住着有寄人篱下感觉的地方", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1474378}, {"id": 305665, "content": "没有热水器的家", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1471454}, {"id": 304898, "content": "没有让我心安的人，让我不快乐的地方，有心累的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1474374}, {"id": 305155, "content": "没有另一半或者父母家人的地方，都不能称为家，只有你爱的人在里面。才是家", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1475320}, {"id": 305667, "content": "宿舍", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1470641}, {"id": 307203, "content": "无时无刻不想逃离", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1427152}, {"id": 304900, "content": "不和谐的家庭生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1472233}, {"id": 305158, "content": "离婚以后，自己搬出来租房住。爸妈不理解，所以父母家不是我家。我晚上回哪里哪里就是家。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1475335}, {"id": 304903, "content": "当然是我自己买的房子啊，不困多大，这才是我自己的港湾（买房后最大的感悟）", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 414097}, {"id": 304904, "content": "有爱的家人或者朋友在", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1263422}, {"id": 304905, "content": "原来的家被强拆了，虽然给了周转房，条件什么的也不差，邻居也还是原来的邻居，还有很多热情的新邻居。\n但，就是感觉这不是家，刚到的一个多月晚上睡觉根本睡不踏实", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1080309}, {"id": 304906, "content": "公司啊！就算加班天天睡在公司，休想让我叫你家", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1161131}, {"id": 305162, "content": "不能放飞自我的地方", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1475341}, {"id": 304908, "content": "租住在北京，每次和别人说回去的时候，总说回住的地方", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1201809}, {"id": 304909, "content": "有亲人的地方才是家啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1474408}, {"id": 304910, "content": "WiFi，网线，舒服的床和厕所是必需品，合适的人是奢侈品", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1474416}, {"id": 304911, "content": "是宿舍啊，睡觉的时候舍友会闹腾，洗衣服洗的晚了就发现两根架子全都满了，生活也没有什么隐私可言", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1474429}, {"id": 304912, "content": "好多人的宿舍呐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1119607}, {"id": 305168, "content": "都在玩手机的地方", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1458877}, {"id": 304914, "content": "有家人 能感到安全感的地方", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1474367}, {"id": 304915, "content": "套用巫师3中一句经典，家不是锁门关窗后一个人待在里边，家是长途跋涉之后到达的地方。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1103227}, {"id": 304916, "content": "如果我可以光脚在一个房间里走动了，就说明我把那个地方当家了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1451284}, {"id": 304917, "content": "宿舍啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1474455}, {"id": 304918, "content": "有爱的人或者睡熟的床", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1430113}, {"id": 305942, "content": "时刻都要带着伪装的面具", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1479472}, {"id": 306454, "content": "不能永久属于我的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1481474}, {"id": 304921, "content": "居住条件太差的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340666}, {"id": 304922, "content": "没有家人的家！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1474477}, {"id": 304923, "content": "压抑却发现自己除了这里没有其他地方可去", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1474492}, {"id": 304924, "content": "不能够随心所欲的支配吧（作息、摆设、私密感）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 689835}, {"id": 304925, "content": "因为有好几个家，不想给别人解释，就不称作家了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 265553}, {"id": 304926, "content": "没有家人的地方\n没有家乡的味道\n没有熟悉的乡音\n", "image": "img/option/option/20181017222505o6wKqQEPGRXtF7yz.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1474513}, {"id": 305182, "content": "学生宿舍之后，公司宿舍", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1475248}, {"id": 304927, "content": "杂乱无章毫无美感且人多口杂的宿舍啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1102081}, {"id": 304928, "content": "回家只是为了睡觉后", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1474518}, {"id": 304929, "content": "有爸妈的地方就是家啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1474520}, {"id": 304930, "content": "没有感情寄托的时候叭", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1144714}, {"id": 304931, "content": "做不到“此处安心是吾乡” 有父母的地方才是家", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1474532}, {"id": 304933, "content": "宿舍啊，和自己不喜欢的人住在一起", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1474552}, {"id": 304935, "content": "不干净", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1443428}, {"id": 304936, "content": "心在漂泊，天地之间就是家", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1389808}, {"id": 304937, "content": "不能让我安心睡眠的地方", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1470426}, {"id": 314665, "content": "没她的地方", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1381070}, {"id": 304938, "content": "不能安心睡眠的地方", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1470426}, {"id": 307242, "content": "没有爸爸妈妈的地方", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1483993}, {"id": 304939, "content": "为了节省房租搬到很小的房间除了床什么都没有 到处都堆满了东西 觉得很乱又无从整理 想快点搬走", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1474572}, {"id": 304940, "content": "手机助手生成的通勤路径的起点", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1254792}, {"id": 304941, "content": "冷清缺乏爱的房子不是家。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1474580}, {"id": 304942, "content": "没有你的情况下", "image": "img/option/option/201810172342132MJpvelkOUqNwECg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1164367}]}